Title: Fix wrong results in view on combined host tag search
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1670419399
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0p18

If you used a combined search with host tags, e.g. "s: MY_SERVICE tg:
MY_AUX_TAG" in the monitoring search, the preview showed the correct result but
the view that was opened on enter showed an incorrect result.
